articles.title: Oregon vs. Texas Tech live updates: Orange Bowl score, CFP highlights - The Register-Guard
articles.description: The Oregon Ducks earned a College Football Playoff quarterfinal win over the Texas Tech Red Raiders. Here are the highlights.
articles.content:
